{"tid":26451,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[租車撚]沖城租車應該點樣揀？","createTime":"2016-12-06T17:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T15:06:47.000Z","uid":25420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d51265ff04c2ac4321d3e6800c8b21ae046e554b","tid":26451,"uid":25420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T17:05:49.000Z","msg":"小毒毒黎緊一月頭會去租車自駕，但係有兩間真係唔太知點揀，自己本身之前有試過兩次台灣自駕，但係日本就未試過，所以想各位巴絲幫手比意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實睇左好多間，最後sort左兩間出黎：Toyota rent-a-car同埋OTS<br />\n<br />\n我見OTS相對較貴，同埋車種無咁多可以揀（4個人得Noah/Fielder），但係佢有Collision Damage Waiver (CDW)同埋Non-operation charges (NOC)，睇落好似就算撞左都比較穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nToyota就平好多，同埋有多小小車款（有Wish/Prius alpha），但就好似得NOC可以選擇加埋，睇落去好似差小小<br />\n<br />\n想睇下大家點樣揀車租，因為兩間野都成日聽到，但又唔熟日本玩法<br />\n<br />\n另外4個大人，租部Prius會唔會太細部？（新款Prius太好J）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nReference:<a href=\"http://www.travelclassroom.net/2011/05/japan-car-rental-insurance.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.travelclassroom.net%2F2011%2F05%2Fjapan-car-rental-insurance.html&d=oMvO6dARAbVNNYonBr5xoJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=7d2a42b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.travelclassroom.net/2011/05/japan-car-rental-insurance.html</a>"},{"pid":"a98da48e2db1a478ccc43879a71f9a8b8aee47bf","tid":26451,"uid":25420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6970aca7f670db90e594ae267e5d7a1dd37655","tid":26451,"uid":4725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:32:33.000Z","msg":"沖城點沖嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4405b786bf48a79bc5970b0618a73fc6ad3d9a46","tid":26451,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:36:12.000Z","msg":"邊度黎?"},{"pid":"0deedefb86fca1cd148564a42a763e649a083f57","tid":26451,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:44:17.000Z","msg":"四月經呢間格價訂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://car.okitour.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcar.okitour.net%2F&d=oMvO6dARAbVNNYonBr5xoJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=90ef24cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://car.okitour.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n經佢訂OTS，平過去官網。<br />\n<br />\n到時去到機場都係同普通OTS訂一樣。<br />\n<br />\n要買全包既保險係到時先揀，會有職員同你講解，乜都包晒要幾錢。"},{"pid":"3755a6e7b695d32ef4773383746d42424539b42a","tid":26451,"uid":33178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:46:17.000Z","msg":"沖城？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 小六畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ddf5da67594f90d63b32522ca3cd71a19977628","tid":26451,"uid":29424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"城你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梗係OTS 抵d啦柒頭， 有40日前/30日前預訂discount 架，唔好就咁禁入去車種睇面價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acef926e77ed1c264679bb098eb2c5eebcc1ae48","tid":26451,"uid":33476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T02:09:29.000Z","msg":"試過nissan 既租車 😯"},{"pid":"2168fabf3f7b10c6677a2f15d7d792bbc1bc9a73","tid":26451,"uid":33476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T02:10:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過nissan 既租車 😯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6個大人 租左果架 細7人車"},{"pid":"b372d50e826ab18eee7e9dbf9503b862b05bd2c3","tid":26451,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T02:15:11.000Z","msg":"沖城都唔識租車，渣ga<br />\n一到步、見到邊架車岩你心水，就叫停架車<br />\n同佢講：<br />\n<br />\n城城城城城城，沖城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你就有免費車<br />\n<br />\n如果問想去沖繩租車玩，等你過18有車牌讀多幾年書先啦"},{"pid":"b742683844352d19a22b701b46f776cfaa4fa99a","tid":26451,"uid":25420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:28:38.000Z","msg":"自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢家先發現自己寫左城市個城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2273233390d15e921afc90c4e228f7cdadccce0","tid":26451,"uid":25420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>城你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梗係OTS 抵d啦柒頭， 有40日前/30日前預訂discount 架，唔好就咁禁入去車種睇面價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係睇完都係要send email過去問佢？"},{"pid":"5b23adfdb4dc7e15a068b0a50765f1b0fd92d4ed","tid":26451,"uid":25420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>四月經呢間格價訂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://car.okitour.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcar.okitour.net%2F&d=oMvO6dARAbVNNYonBr5xoJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=90ef24cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://car.okitour.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n經佢訂OTS，平過去官網。<br />\n<br />\n到時去到機場都係同普通OTS訂一樣。<br />\n<br />\n要買全包既保險係到時先揀，會有職員同你講解，乜都包晒要幾錢。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢間野係咪中介咁樣，見佢有好多間公司都有做<br />\n<br />\n保險其實一般需要買到去邊個位？"},{"pid":"fab30ada6a2cdb1006221eaa94d8bf19b4ba7bed","tid":26451,"uid":29424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:23:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>城你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梗係OTS 抵d啦柒頭， 有40日前/30日前預訂discount 架，唔好就咁禁入去車種睇面價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係睇完都係要send email過去問佢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直接揀拎車日子地點時間，還車地點時間，入到去個畫面拉底少少就會見到40日前預約折扣plan <br />\n<br />\n有得揀的話強烈建議揀Aqua , 又靜又慳油<br />\n<br />\n利申：我用日文官網訂，如果中文無出你試埋日文官網先，我訂過6、7次"},{"pid":"4368275cf4a345c9c6c6d7f70e0035a6c40f31b0","tid":26451,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:36:50.000Z","msg":"on9問題"},{"pid":"4ee7437149210fd50857325a1dfce3456c6eeeb1","tid":26451,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"我睇你個人本身都on99<br />\n咪渣車啦<br />\n害死人呀"},{"pid":"3ad5f43f2d4fcfc689cae7f401100bfc0e9fbe6b","tid":26451,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:48:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>四月經呢間格價訂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://car.okitour.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcar.okitour.net%2F&d=oMvO6dARAbVNNYonBr5xoJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=90ef24cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://car.okitour.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經佢訂OTS，平過去官網。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到時去到機場都係同普通OTS訂一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要買全包既保險係到時先揀，會有職員同你講解，乜都包晒要幾錢。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢間野係咪中介咁樣，見佢有好多間公司都有做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保險其實一般需要買到去邊個位？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知佢點構做，似格價網咁，乜都係去到先俾，DEPOSIT都唔洗。<br />\n<br />\n你想包到連刮花都包咪去到再加，連爆軚都包埋有人同你過嚟整。<br />\n<br />\n我記錯，應該係租歐力士，唔係OTS。"},{"pid":"af7d5b28c2f8948aad2117724163d1dfca43dc0e","tid":26451,"uid":25420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>城你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梗係OTS 抵d啦柒頭， 有40日前/30日前預訂discount 架，唔好就咁禁入去車種睇面價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係睇完都係要send email過去問佢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直接揀拎車日子地點時間，還車地點時間，入到去個畫面拉底少少就會見到40日前預約折扣plan <br />\n<br />\n有得揀的話強烈建議揀Aqua , 又靜又慳油<br />\n<br />\n利申：我用日文官網訂，如果中文無出你試埋日文官網先，我訂過6、7次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n四個大人，Aqua好似唔多夠位<br />\n但係想揀Hybrid車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日文官網會唔會到時一定要識講日文先比你租"},{"pid":"700d9b18aeb7dcbebf3e8fa7388671c3d859e1d8","tid":26451,"uid":25420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>四月經呢間格價訂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://car.okitour.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcar.okitour.net%2F&d=oMvO6dARAbVNNYonBr5xoJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=90ef24cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://car.okitour.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經佢訂OTS，平過去官網。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到時去到機場都係同普通OTS訂一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要買全包既保險係到時先揀，會有職員同你講解，乜都包晒要幾錢。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢間野係咪中介咁樣，見佢有好多間公司都有做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保險其實一般需要買到去邊個位？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知佢點構做，似格價網咁，乜都係去到先俾，DEPOSIT都唔洗。<br />\n<br />\n你想包到連刮花都包咪去到再加，連爆軚都包埋有人同你過嚟整。<br />\n<br />\n我記錯，應該係租歐力士，唔係OTS。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b27728cd65397fcef537a76cca1c74d7316b83d","tid":26451,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>城你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梗係OTS 抵d啦柒頭， 有40日前/30日前預訂discount 架，唔好就咁禁入去車種睇面價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係睇完都係要send email過去問佢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直接揀拎車日子地點時間，還車地點時間，入到去個畫面拉底少少就會見到40日前預約折扣plan <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有得揀的話強烈建議揀Aqua , 又靜又慳油<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我用日文官網訂，如果中文無出你試埋日文官網先，我訂過6、7次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四個大人，Aqua好似唔多夠位<br />\n<br />\n但係想揀Hybrid車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日文官網會唔會到時一定要識講日文先比你租</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你搵歐力士同OTS，點都會識少少英文既，GPS 都有埋中文MENU，但係會廢過英文，有啲漢化做得差，變佐某啲功能無佐。<br />\n<br />\n歐力士租車，要坐SHUTTLE 去車場，有個職員跟車，英文就差唔多唔識，都係大家估下估下對方講乜，總算溝通得到。<br />\n<br />\n去到車場就COUNTER同攞車都可以用英文。"},{"pid":"17c42729a84b7627fbd137c2b4c299964123c003","tid":26451,"uid":30272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:41:24.000Z","msg":"Orix 最抵"},{"pid":"33f9a7e05d0e9ad9e0db5d1eb3c36a34cfb2ea56","tid":26451,"uid":25420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"另外問題：保險買到幾多先夠？<br />\n雖然買得多實有多啲保障，不過價錢又貴，所以想參考下巴絲意見，攞個平衡"},{"pid":"c3378c83d0079fabbb310f18d0b73637272882fd","tid":26451,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:53:40.000Z","msg":"唔知應該點答你問題<br />\n你想渣prius咪睇下邊間平啲<br />\n<br />\n係日本撞得車你應該真該真係好廢/好唔彩下<br />\n<br />\n上次去沖繩租左架serena渣<br />\n幾好係啲公路會有時幾大風"},{"pid":"cb596a8397777962ee4f79475997c5fa474bad2d","tid":26451,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:06:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外問題：保險買到幾多先夠？<br />\n雖然買得多實有多啲保障，不過價錢又貴，所以想參考下巴絲意見，攞個平衡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定要買果份，就有墊底費<br />\n<br />\n再加果份就連墊底都包埋<br />\n<br />\n你自己計風驗囉。"}]}